         <abstract id="aspace_65af5cbc754bd8cc68488a4345e61919">This collection contains examples of graphic art, primarily before 1800. Many of these materials are not dated; an educated guess as to the age of the material was based on paper type and subject matter.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_021e8ec888bed7e46b4312b868eea460">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Collection of Early Graphic Art was housed in the former Arts of the Book Collection until its transfer to the Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library in 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_422972762490311d38a74acee95f5cb7">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_13c3cdc7a0b90fca6b76f55af42cae66">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_61be4d055780014e329cd133f4fcdd2b">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Collection of Early Graphic Art, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_f81d776cbfee43915e1ebcbd39734cc6">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains examples of graphic art, primarily before 1800. Many of these materials are not dated; an educated guess as to the age of the material was based on paper type and subject matter.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_1e52cf32018635d7e5bd00646e4f94a8">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into five series: I. Figurative. II. Typography. III. Landscape &amp; Architecture. IV. Nature. V. Ornamentation.</p>  
      </arrangement>
